OL,5, Dr Jo Wilson was a respected           
OL,6, international businesswoman and author 
OL,7, when she was diagnosed with dementia in
OL,8, 2020 at the age of 66. Following her   
OL,9, death, the BBC caught up with her      
OL,10, husband to discuss his campaign        
OL,11, inspired by her.                       
OL,13,F"I want the whole world to talk about  
OL,14,Fdementia," Bill Wilson says, adding:   
OL,15,F"I'm really not going to be happy until
OL,16,Fthat happens."                         
OL,18,FSince losing his wife in January, Bill 
OL,19,Fhas made it his mission to campaign for
OL,20,Fbetter understanding of the disease.   
